@startuml
title Crypto Summary - Keys, Signing and Verification

participant Issuer as I
participant Holder as H
participant Verifier as V

I -> I : Generate Ed25519 key pair
I -> I : Store private key securely
I -> I : Publish public key in DID Document

H -> H : Generate own Ed25519 key pair
H -> H : Sign Verifiable Presentation using private key

V -> V : Resolve DID Documents
V -> V : Verify VC and VP signatures using public keys

note right of I
Issuer Operations:
- Generates Ed25519 key pair
- Signs Verifiable Credential (VC)
- Publishes public key in DID Document
end note

note right of H
Holder Operations:
- Generates Ed25519 key pair
- Signs Verifiable Presentation (VP)
- Reveals selected claims only
end note

note right of V
Verifier Operations:
- Resolves DID Documents
- Verifies VC and VP signatures using public keys
end note

@enduml
